WEBVTT

1
00:02.500 --> 00:05.620
You don't have to hold it all together.

2
00:11.500 --> 00:16.140
The friction is just exhaustion. Let the rigid lines fail.

3
00:18.000 --> 00:23.840
See? It doesn't collapse. It just settles into where it actually belongs.

4
00:27.500 --> 00:30.500
Quiet now. The work is done.

